content:
Refresh Data More Frequently with Incremental Refresh in BYOL Data Federation

Access only new or updated data from a third-party partner, reducing latency and cost. You no longer need to perform a full refresh to update your data. With incremental refresh, you can update your data every 15 mins to 7 days as opposed to every 4 hrs to 7 days.

When: This feature is being rolled out in August 2024.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

Salesforce Help: BYOL Data Federation
Salesforce Help: Acceleration in Data Federation
